                "invention-title": [
                    "Continuous production method of phenyl trichlorosilane",
                    "一种苯基三氯硅烷的连续化生产方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a continuous production method of phenyl trichlorosilane. A palladium catalyst Pd-MCl3 is adopted in the reaction, wherein M is B, Zn or Fe; the catalyst is combined with hydrogen free radicals decomposed from trichlorosilane to promote an electrophilic substitution reaction of chlorobenzene; a tubular reactor is adopted, raw materials and products pass through a tube pass, and nitrogen is used as a heating and cooling medium to pass through a shell pass; the reactor divides a shell pass into six sections including a preheating section, a first reaction chamber, a cooling section, a second reaction chamber, a cooling section and a third reaction chamber from bottom to top, the six sections are mutually isolated through fixed tube plates and are equal in vertical length, and each section is provided with a gas inlet and a gas outlet. Nitrogen is adopted as a heating and cooling medium of the reactor, so that the energy consumption of the reactor is further reduced, and the phenyl trichlorosilane product with the mass fraction of 99.9% or above and the chlorobenzene content, the trichlorosilane content, the tetrachlorosilane content, the benzene content, the hydrogen chloride content, the high-boiling residue content and the solid residue content of less than 1 ppm can be obtained."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种苯基三氯硅烷的连续化生产方法。反应采用钯系催化剂Pd‑MCl3，其中M＝B、Zn、Fe；催化剂与三氯氢硅分解出的氢自由基结合，促进氯苯的亲电取代反应；采用管式反应器，原料和产物走管程，使用氮气作为加热和冷却介质走壳程；反应器将壳程从下到上分为预热段、第一反应室、冷却段、第二反应室、冷却段及第三反应室共六段，六段通过固定管板互相隔绝且上下长度相等，每段分别开有气体入口和出口。采用氮气作为反应器的加热和冷却介质，进一步降低了反应器能耗，能够获得质量分率达99.9％以上，氯苯含量、三氯氢硅含量、四氯氢硅含量、苯含量、氯化氢含量、高沸物含量和固体残渣含量均小于1ppm的苯基三氯硅烷产物。"
                }
            ]
